    },
    {
      "num": 2,
      "title": "その患者、本当にDKAではない？",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "起：血糖が正常だからDKAを除外していませんか？",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:30px}.alert-box{border-left:6px solid #14b8a6;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.08);padding:30px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-bottom:24px}.alert-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:24px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:20px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 2 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>その患者、本当にDKAではない？</h2><div class=\"alert-box\"><p>SGLT2阻害薬を服用中の患者が<br>悪心・嘔吐・腹痛・倦怠感で救急搬送<br>血糖値は180 mg/dL<br>「血糖が正常だからDKAではないだろう」</p></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>その判断が、致命的な診断の遅れにつながります<br>SGLT2阻害薬では血糖250未満でもDKAが起こり得ます</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 3,
      "title": "正常血糖DKAの疫学データ",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "承：発生率と臨床症状のエビデンス",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.card{border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 30px;margin-bottom:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.card-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:8px}.card-body{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.highlight{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700}.source{font-size:18px;color:#64748b;margin-top:16px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 3 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>正常血糖DKAの疫学データ</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">発生率</div><div class=\"card-body\">SGLT2阻害薬使用者のDKA発生率：<span class=\"highlight\">0.1〜0.3%</span><br>周術期（待機手術）：<span class=\"highlight\">0.17%</span> / 緊急手術：<span class=\"highlight\">1.1%</span><br>術後30日以内のDKAリスク：非使用者の<span class=\"highlight\">6倍</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">臨床症状（Lee 2025 メタアナリシス / 9研究）</div><div class=\"card-body\">悪心・嘔吐 <span class=\"highlight\">57.9〜76.5%</span> / 腹痛 <span class=\"highlight\">42.1〜83.3%</span><br>発熱 16.7〜50.0% / 呼吸困難 16.7〜21.1%<br>意識障害 12.5〜29.4%</div></div><div class=\"source\">出典：Lee J, et al. Diabetes Obes Metab 2025; StatPearls 2024</div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 4,
      "title": "なぜ血糖が正常なのにDKAになるのか",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "転：SGLT2阻害薬特有のメカニズム",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:24px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:18px}.list-num{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6;min-width:50px;margin-right:16px}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:20px 30px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:20px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 4 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>なぜ血糖正常でDKAになるのか</h2><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">1</span><span class=\"list-text\">SGLT2阻害薬により尿糖排泄が増加し、血糖が低下</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">2</span><span class=\"list-text\">血糖低下に伴いインスリン分泌が減少</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">3</span><span class=\"list-text\">膵α細胞への直接作用でグルカゴン分泌が亢進</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">4</span><span class=\"list-text\">インスリン/グルカゴン比が低下し、肝臓でケトン体産生が増加</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">5</span><span class=\"list-text\">血糖は尿糖排泄で上がらず「高血糖」の警告サインが消失</span></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>血糖を下げる薬効そのものが、DKAの発見を妨げる</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 5,
      "title": "診断と治療のポイント",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "結：見逃さないための具体的アクション",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;gap:30px;align-items:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:20px}.col{flex:1}.card{border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.card-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:8px}.card-body{font-size:24px;line-height:1.5;color:#334155}.highlight{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 5 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"col\"><h2>診断基準</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\">動脈血pH <span class=\"highlight\">< 7.3</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\">血清重炭酸 <span class=\"highlight\">< 18 mEq/L</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\">アニオンギャップ <span class=\"highlight\">> 12</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\">血中βHB <span class=\"highlight\">> 3.0 mmol/L</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\">血糖 <span class=\"highlight\">< 250 mg/dL</span></div></div></div><div style=\"width:2px;background:#14b8a6;height:80%;opacity:0.3\"></div><div class=\"col\"><h2>治療の要点</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">1. SGLT2阻害薬の即時中止</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">2. 十分な輸液（生食）</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">3. インスリン持続静注 + ブドウ糖液</div><div class=\"card-body\">最初から5-10%ブドウ糖液を併用</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">4. モニタリング指標</div><div class=\"card-body\">血糖ではなく<span class=\"highlight\">ケトン体・AG・pH</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 6,
      "title": "Take Home Message",
      "style": "accent",
      "content": "3つの持ち帰りポイント",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px}.thm-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 36px;margin-bottom:24px;display:flex;align-items:center}.thm-num{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-right:24px;min-width:50px;opacity:0.7}.thm-text{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.5}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 6 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>Take Home Message</h2><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">01</span><span class=\"thm-text\">「血糖正常 = DKAなし」は禁句<br>SGLT2阻害薬使用中は血糖に関係なく血液ガス+血中ケトン体を</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">02</span><span class=\"thm-text\">シックデイは必ず休薬、手術前3日から中止<br>これが最大の予防策</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">03</span><span class=\"thm-text\">治療は最初からブドウ糖液+インスリン持続静注<br>モニタリング指標は血糖ではなくケトン体・AG・pH</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 7,
      "title": "参考文献",
